import React from 'react'; import { useQuery } from 'react-query'; import { tradeAPI, expenseAPI, goalAPI } from '../services/api'; import { CurrencyDollarIcon, TrendingUpIcon, TrendingDownIcon, ChartBarIcon, TargetIcon } from '@heroicons/react/24/outline'; import { format } from 'date-fns'; const Dashboard = () => { const { data: portfolio } = useQuery('portfolio', tradeAPI.getPortfolio); const { data: expenses } = useQuery('expenses', expenseAPI.getAll); const { data: goals } = useQuery('goals', goalAPI.getActive); const totalExpenses = expenses?.reduce((sum, expense) => sum + parseFloat(expense.amount), 0) || 0; const totalInvested = portfolio?.totalInvested || 0; const currentValue = portfolio?.currentValue || 0; const totalProfitLoss = portfolio?.totalProfitLoss || 0; const activeGoals = goals?.length || 0; const stats = [ { name: 'Total Invested', value: `$${totalInvested.toLocaleString()}`, icon: CurrencyDollarIcon, color: 'bg-blue-500', }, { name: 'Current Value', value: `$${currentValue.toLocaleString()}`, icon: TrendingUpIcon, color: 'bg-green-500', }, { name: 'Total P&L', value: `$${totalProfitLoss.toLocaleString()}`, icon: totalProfitLoss >= 0 ? TrendingUpIcon : TrendingDownIcon, color: totalProfitLoss >= 0 ? 'bg-green-500' : 'bg-red-500', }, { name: 'Total Expenses', value: `$${totalExpenses.toLocaleString()}`, icon: ChartBarIcon, color: 'bg-yellow-500', }, { name: 'Active Goals', value: activeGoals.toString(), icon: TargetIcon, color: 'bg-purple-500', }, ]; return (

Dashboard

Welcome back! Here's your financial overview.

{/* Stats Grid */}
{stats.map((stat) => (

{stat.name}

{stat.value}

))}
{/* Recent Activity */}
{/* Recent Trades */}

Recent Trades

{expenses?.slice(0, 5).map((expense) => (

{expense.description}

{format(new Date(expense.expenseDate), 'MMM dd, yyyy')}

${parseFloat(expense.amount).toFixed(2)}
))}
{/* Active Goals */}

Active Goals

{goals?.slice(0, 5).map((goal) => (

{goal.name}

{Math.round( (parseFloat(goal.currentAmount) / parseFloat(goal.targetAmount)) * 100 )}%

${parseFloat(goal.currentAmount).toFixed(2)}

of ${parseFloat(goal.targetAmount).toFixed(2)}

))}
{/* Quick Actions */}

Quick Actions

); }; export default Dashboard;
